tail != null;\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * @return The specified log detail or <code>null</code> if undefined\n     */\n    public LogDetail getLogDetail() {\n\n[46 more lines in file. Use offset=261 to continue.]"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1780952963989}]}
